Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:12.15,OP,,0,0,0,,在心灵的街道中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:18.50,OP,,0,0,0,,闪耀着希望之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.10,0:00:24.70,OP,,0,0,0,,用虚幻的羽翼挥动着梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:30.95,OP,,0,0,0,,是你与我寻找的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:47.47,OP,,0,0,0,,真理总是隐藏在眼中 蓝蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:54.32,OP,,0,0,0,,我们要往何处去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:01:01.12,OP,,0,0,0,,俩人未来与现今的流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:06.75,OP,,0,0,0,,我们继续踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:13.62,OP,,0,0,0,,永远的目标地 无止尽的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:24.62,OP,,0,0,0,,希望能不放手不断追寻 直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫日暮戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生于一个\N历史很悠久很古老的神社里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个非常平凡的国三女生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就在我十五岁生日那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社的井里\N突然出现了一个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我带回到了战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那里\N遇到了一个半妖少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有\N可以增强妖怪法力的宝玉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了跟犬夜叉他们\N一起寻找散落各处的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开始来往于\N现代与战国之间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想借四魂之玉的力量\N满足自己的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫奈落的妖怪为了从\N犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到完美的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意将杀生丸引进奈落城里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正当奈落打算吞了杀生丸\N将他化成自己的一部分的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉偏偏破了奈落的结界\N跑进奈落城来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的  风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的结界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在千钧一发之际\N救兵及时赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真以为一辈子\N都能逃出我的手掌心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落利用珊瑚的弟弟\N琥珀做他的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁机逃之夭夭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此\N真的从我们的面前消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第82话 奔波于现代与战国之间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可恶了  奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道以后\N他都不再回这座城了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连结界都被你破除了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他又怎么能搬走这座城堡呢\N你说对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再给我一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定\N真的可以砍死奈落这个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏就差那么一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\N总算又可以回到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算回到了这个安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻松松的念书了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想\N还真有点对不起犬夜叉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得大家现在好不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个公式  后天一定会考哦\N大家回去要牢牢的把它背住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟考
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都什么时候了\N还在担心别人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩两天\N要是不赶快抱抱佛脚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候恐怕要补考那就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  可以走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你啦  借我笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们自己也要复习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托拜托一下下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只借一下下\N就还给你们总可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  谁叫你这么弱不禁风\N一天到晚生病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又是你最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道你们一定会帮我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就拿去影印一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就还给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得这么可怜\N我们哪敢不借呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就谢谢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家开动吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在胡思乱想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想什么还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是那个\N爱吃醋的小太保是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想别的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟他到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事到底怎么样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你发展到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天才见过他哥哥而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说见过他哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他哥哥恐怕也是太保吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他哥哥这么凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他哥哥应该更厉害一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们兄弟俩只要一碰面\N经常都会打架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两兄弟都不是好惹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:17.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你打算继续这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心你将来吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒认为\N爱可以克服一切障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇我支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我借走笔记了  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大学生正在考试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的目的都跟戈薇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么办?要去排队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是影印去哪里都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到其他地方去印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么到处都这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞么鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝…祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是些没有义气的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这家伙\N不晓得为什么去那么久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说好了\N马上就会回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对\N她说过要待两三天才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.83,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么每一个人\N都好像没事一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落从我们手中跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是第一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更别说是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你也应该养足精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才有力气继续对付奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不像你们几个家伙\N这么不堪一击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不觉得疲倦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那种打法\N普通人还真是受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己身子差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好意思怪别人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落的邪气还阴魂不散呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来都让那些死魂虫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙寻找他那股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次偏偏\N连结界的位置都感应不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底奈落那股邪气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上从琥珀身上\N取下四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你只当\N这个小子是个傀儡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就不会\N帮你解决那个人质姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会送上门让杀生丸杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再这么继续反抗奈落下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看\N你恐怕没多少日子可活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光会说别人  而我自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.14,0:09:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连琥珀也一起不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来弥勒法师\N特地去安慰珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇早就跟我说过\N珊瑚一定在偷偷期待琥珀回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母  我可以坐一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子你还在担心\N你弟弟的事对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么说有点强人所难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.82,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你真的要放宽心才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我能够了解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候\N你是不是想一个人静一静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要说的就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  弥勒法师最恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假装要安慰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是想趁机吃豆腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.82,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天等很久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不早点跟我说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的声音特别清脆好听
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个都只会偷懒\N一点都不知道上进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N还是得自己挑灯夜战了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一点都看不懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  请问哲子在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在电话里问问也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚在电话里面问了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  你的课本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果昨天一整天\N什么都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  姐姐  告诉你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要打断我听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易背住了\N又让你给打断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天再背不起来的话\N真的会完蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是专程来接你的  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  马上跟我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不要捣乱好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就要考试了你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又发什么小姐脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我乖乖的  知不知道\N绝对不可以到外头去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖待在家里你听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  我傍晚就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇忘了把便当带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不晓得能不能麻烦你跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要沿着戈薇身上的气味找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很快可以追上她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮忙  马上给我抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚  全都给我闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子\N你活得不耐烦了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来戈薇她们这个时代\N也安全不到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在发什么呆啊  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耳朵好可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.31,0:14:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥哥  谢谢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要命\N这世界怎么乱成这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事啊  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉怎么会在这里出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是你叫坐下的吧\N麻烦你站起来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.28,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出门前不是跟你说过\N叫你千万不要出门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有人托我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人托你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的便当耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道专程替我送便当来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们分着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都挤成一堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在家里温书\N根本就没有办法专心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子\N只好在图书馆待到天黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快点念就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肋间神经痛好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年纪轻轻居然身体那么差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要好好锻炼才行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一些对健康有益的食谱\N是我特别搜集来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿回去试一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.31,0:16:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条这个人真的好细心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚怎么没有想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然忘了跟北条借笔记来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.85,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  突然想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个中药偏方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说对各种病都很有帮助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  戈薇同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体健康呢最重要的是情绪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要让自己的生活有规律
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三餐也要定时定量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇同学  记得一定要吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  北条同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真倒霉  还是没有借到笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刚刚说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一位\N身穿红衣身轻如燕的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后紧要关头\N帮忙抓到了强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.00,0:18:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位年轻人的\N英勇事迹不只这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还帮消防队\N救出被困在大火中的小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:24.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那位年轻人的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是刚刚我戴的帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去学校之前你到底做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别说这些  这盒子装什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书都念不完了  还在吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草太  你进来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐  什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我陪犬夜叉哥哥玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉哥哥  我们去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续看书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好烫  搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不能出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂都还没有冲掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不玩了\N出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你出去你听到了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公式又忘得一干二净了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我们一起吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.76,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算安静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头快烧掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了咖哩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是辣到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你自己像饿死鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到东西就往嘴里塞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫什么叫\N你很烦知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样一直看着我\N我会分心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你还是躺下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己笨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你眼睛不看着前面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了\N明天可以跟我回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子\N难道打算整晚都盯着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.22,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么精力充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡  睡着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不晓得这小子搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家要温书偏偏来搅局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉这副熟睡的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.82,0:21:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前还真的没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最忙最累的一向就是他嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少今天晚上\N你可以好好的睡一觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你昨天晚上\N在戈薇家过夜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了?戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.72,0:21:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫你昨天晚上\N整晚都霸占我的床
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.06,0:22:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我连模拟考都考砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.43,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可恶的人就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.75,0:22:21.35,ED,,0,0,0,,究竟要流多少泪{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:28.20,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 才能坦白面对自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:35.02,ED,,0,0,0,,倘若对谁传达情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:42.02,ED,,0,0,0,,Every Heart 是否就能得到满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:48.32,ED,,0,0,0,,害怕着漫长漫长的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:55.40,ED,,0,0,0,,朝着遥远的星星祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:23:02.15,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:08.77,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找真正的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:15.82,ED,,0,0,0,,希望自己能够变得更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:22.50,ED,,0,0,0,,今天也要抬头看着高高的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:29.12,ED,,0,0,0,,在不停流转的时空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:35.75,ED,,0,0,0,,我们都在寻找生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:39.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始发问
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片  根本不在奈落手里\N你说会是谁拿走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.48,0:23:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我数数\N在琥珀背上有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇手里还有三个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:23:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.45,0:23:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停  时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族的钢牙\N两只脚上也有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一钢牙也被奈落抓到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点你放心  奈落现在不知道\N躲到什么地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?这又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.49,0:24:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族少女和月虹的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.93,0:24:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说妖狼族少女
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别忘了还有钢牙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉宝典
